      body {
        font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
        color: #111;
      }

      h1 {
        position: relative;
        font-family: "Athiti", sans-serif;
        color: #5ac116;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      h2 {
        font-family: "Athiti", sans-serif;
        color: #5ac116;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 200px;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
      }

      .eagle {
        width: 30px;
        height: auto;
        display: inline;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Última aula disponível, <%= name %>!</h1>
    <p>
      Olá, <%= name %>! Se quiser reassistir a aula do dia <%= formattedDate %>,
      ela está disponível no portal!
    </p>
    <p>
      Clique
      <a href="https://portal.arthurvincent.com.br/my-classes" target="_blank"
        >aqui</a
      >
      para acessar a aula pelo portal!
    </p>
    <p>
      Lembre-se do seu Homework, revise o Anki e, precisando, reveja a aula!
      <%= name %>
    </p>
    <p>Teacher Arthur!</p>
    <h1>Last class available, <%= name %>!</h1>
    <p>
      Hello, <%= name %>! If you want to rewatch the class of the day <%=
      formattedDate %>, it is available on the portal!
    </p>
    <p>
      Click
      <a href="https://portal.arthurvincent.com.br/my-classes" target="_blank"
        >here</a
      >
      to access the class via the portal!
    </p>
    <p>
      Remember your Homework, review Anki and, if necessary, review the class!
      <%= name %>
    </p>
    <p>Teacher Arthur!</p>
    <img
      class="logo"
      src="https://ik.imagekit.io/vjz75qw96/assets/mylogotransp.png?updatedAt=1715968430436"
      alt="arvinlogo"
    />
  </body>
</html>
